    "Then I'll overview my MILA talk.",
    "And last, I'll ask you to summarize your understanding of it (and any criticisms or objections you may have).",
    "The first and most important distinction: This used to be called the distinction between \"artificial intelligence\" (AI) and \"cognitive modelling\" (CM).",
    "\"AI\" was taken to be the creation of artificial tools to be used by humans, and CM was taken to be the attempt to reverse-engineer the causal mechanisms that produce human cognitive capacity.",
    "Both are now part of \"cognitive science.\""
